TEXT(beginproblem());


BEGIN_TEXT
Find the values of \(x\) so that the series below converges.
\[
    \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{$a}{x^n}
\]

$BR 
Give your answer in \{ helpLink('interval notation')\}.
$BR 
$BR 

Answer: \{ans_rule(20)\}
END_TEXT

ANS(Interval('(-infinity, -1)U(1, infinity)')->cmp('showEndTypeHints' => 1));

